                    <history>
                      <origin>
                          This document most likely constitutes the script of a lecture <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7812Peterman"> Julius Heinrich Petermann </persName> held at the ‘Berliner Akademie’ on 5 May 1873, 
                          see  <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PHT474WK"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Praetorius1887Review"/><title level="a">Review of Manuel de la lange tigraï parlée au centre et dans le nord de l'Abyssinie by Jules Schreiber</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift der Deutschen Morgenländischen Gesellschaft</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Franz</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Praetorius</t:surname></author><date>1887</date><biblScope unit="volume">41</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">4</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">685-691</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">686</citedRange></bibl>
                          and <bibl><ptr target="bm:AdW1873Monatsberichte"/><citedRange unit="page">300</citedRange></bibl>. It can therefore be assumed that it was
                          written by <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7812Peterman"> Julius Heinrich Petermann </persName> in <origDate when="1873">1873</origDate>.
                      </origin>
                        <provenance>Together with other documents belonging to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7812Peterman"> Julius Heinrich Petermann </persName>, this script passed to  
                            <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS7939Praetori">Franz Praetorius</persName> after the former’s death, see <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PHT474WK"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Praetorius1887Review"/><title level="a">Review of Manuel de la lange tigraï parlée au centre et dans le nord de l'Abyssinie by Jules Schreiber</title><title level="j">Zeitschrift der Deutschen Morgenländischen Gesellschaft</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Franz</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Praetorius</t:surname></author><date>1887</date><biblScope unit="volume">41</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">4</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">685-691</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">685–686</citedRange></bibl>.</provenance>
                        <acquisition>This document is kept together with other documents as part of the ‘Nachlass Praetorius’ (shelfmark DMG Yi 135) at
